The '''''British Kaffrarian Government Gazette''''' was the [[government gazette]] of [[British Kaffraria]]. It was published in the 1860s<ref name="Walker1963">{{cite book|last=Walker|first=Eric Anderson|title=The Cambridge History of the British Empire|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ISg9AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA909|year=1963|publisher=CUP Archive|page=909|id=GGKEY:J4RZC934KC3}}</ref> during the brief period for which British Kaffraria was a [[Crown Colony]] (1860–1866).

