'''Hit FM''' is a [[radio station]] in [[Jutland]], [[Denmark]]. It is divided into three stations, each of which broadcast on their own frequency. There are local departments in [[Aalborg]], [[Viborg, Denmark|Viborg]] and [[Herning]].

The station plays a variety of genres, including [[pop music|pop]], [[rock music|rock]], [[hip hop]] and [[R&B]]. Within these genres, the station focuses on popular [[mainstream]] hits.

