The '''Jewel of Russia Festival''' is an annual international celebration of music, opera, literature, and arts. It takes place at the [[Hermitage Museum]], [[Mariinsky Theatre]] and Museum of Ethnography in [[St Petersburg]], [[Russia]]. The festival is directed by Pablo Ganguli.

