'''Mazomba''' is a giant [[fish]] in the [[mythology]] of the [[Chaga]] people of [[Tanzania]].<ref>[[The Mythology of All Races]] (13 vols.), edited by [[Louis Herbert Gray]] and George Foot Moore; Cooper Square Publishers, Inc., New York, 1964.</ref> It is also the name of a crater on [[Triton (moon)|Triton]], a moon of [[Neptune]].<ref>{{GPN|3771|Mazomba}}</ref>

